===Preposition===
'''к''' ''+ [[dative case]]'' ('''[[ко]]''' before words beginning with certain awkward consonant clusters such as '''мн-''', '''вс-''', '''вт-''', and '''сн-'''.)

# [[to]], [[toward]]
#: к {{l|ru|дом|дому}} — ''to the house''
#: к {{l|ru|брат|брату}} — ''to my brother''
#: ко {{l|ru|я|мне}} — ''to me''
# ''(time)'': [[by]], [[for]]
#: ко {{l|ru|вторник|вторнику}} — ''by Tuesday, for Tuesday''

