=====Usage notes=====
Although both {{term|к|lang=sh}} and {{term|ка|lang=sh}} can be used synonymously, {{term|к|lang=sh}} must take the alternative form {{term|ка|lang=sh}} in the following environment:
* before /к, г, х/:
*: ''ка граду'' - to the city
*: ''ка горе'' - towards above
*: ''ка хладу'' - toward the shade

